betterquesting:10.desc:8: Congradulations Intern! You and several others have been sent to this planet to prove your worthyness. If you prove yourself not only do you get a raise but the chance to earn a paycheck. By going to this dimension you have agreed to the Science, Acquisitions, and Defense (SAD) test. By checking this box you are unlocking the questbook, so expect a notification spam
Go get some wood, you know, trees... Please dont say you lost your memory on transport...
Whats the Plural for Furnace? Furni? Furnaces?
Alot of keybinds are taken over. Here are a list you should prbably change...
Ores... You are gonna need to go mining....
Getting Suited up for the war ahead
Pulverising ores for the future! Or more ore... That works..
Powered Furnace, never'd see the day...
Every machine needs a frame! Well not everyone...
No not 'Photo'genic... Its all about the sun not images

Just for the shear reason to tangle yourself in water! Wait thats not how that works?
Solid fuel goes in, power comes out!

The turbine conversion allows you to make steam and use that steam to make more power than using one Steam Dynamo, place a Steam Dynamo With the Boil Augment next to a Steam Dynamo with the Turbine Augment, Viola more power, just make sure you got water to fuel it
Each Augment is self explanitory, just hold shift.
Fun? There is no fun when there are WITHERS

Good way to store all that food and ores from mining.

Just place them and rightclick for a ride!

By now you may have noticed Spice Of Life is in here, yah about now would be a good time to get a stable variety of food. Perhaps some Pams would help? Pams Gardens are rare so have some at the cost of a bit of dirt.
With this being powered and a prick of your finger you can make a clone! In 5 short minutes
The Sync Chamber needs to be powered a very special way, called running. Place a treadmill against the side of 'pod'. use the pig to run on the treadmill. I call him Jeffery...
There are ALOT of bits in a single block. Might need a bag
Tech Guns 2, one of your lines of defence
Full Prptection requires a full suit. To make it work you ahve to use an Air Compressor to fill the chestplate with air.
You already forgot what SAD is? Science, Acquisitions, and Defense (SAD) is a test in which you score points based on these 3 catagories. Go make someone proud, in failure or in success
You need food, if you havnt been able to clear a building or find a good sorce of food here we go.
Storage for your clones is needed in order to swap to each one.
Bit by bit you can slowly annoy GrimCo
